**Path 1 — Buy STM32F407 (~$50)**
OpenFFBoard STM32F407 → CAN → Flipsky VESC → hoverboard/G30 motor

**Path 2 — AFFBWheel, no STM32 needed**
ACEBOTT Leonardo → UART → Flipsky VESC → hoverboard/G30 motor

